Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}本当に現実なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:09.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}心がまだ追いついて来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}今は想像出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:17.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}この先押し寄せる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:21.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}Still,I have to keep going this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}あなたが居ない世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}miss you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}消えないこの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}会いたいあの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:38.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}もう一度近づきたい話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I know life can be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:48.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}最後の言葉をねぇちゃんと聞かせてよ
