Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}It's sad to say goodbye.
