Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:09.35,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我的心還來不及認清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.02,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}眼下還無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:17.27,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}這奔湧而來的痛楚
