Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.57,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}在這沒有了你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.28,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我是如此想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}這永不消弭的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.92,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}多想再見到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:38.21,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}想再一次貼近你 與你歡談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.13,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我已知曉 生命竟能如此煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:48.39,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}你最後的話語 我多麼想要聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:52.43,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}只願你能與我相伴
