Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:00.32,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}我的生命不能沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:04.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}奉獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:11.33,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}是時候與你說再見了
